服务器开发说明
1，install mysql database and open the port of mysql to the internet, because we need the port when develop and debug in internet.
you need to close the port 3306 if deploy to a real environment

2, install redis and open the port of redis, ohter is to do the same with mysql

三，安装python3,并且根据requirement.txt安装相应依赖库
3, install python3 and pip3.
pip install -r requirement.txt